data.description: Situated in the picturesque community of Flat Rock Hills, this expansive ranch-style residence at 4220 Sawgrass Dr, Lithonia, GA 30038, offers a spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath layout with a generous 2010 square feet of living area. Beyond its charming facade, this well-maintained home reveals a welcoming interior, creating an atmosphere of comfort and ease. The property features a gourmet kitchen, complete with a kitchen island, providing both style and functionality. Its convenient location in a lovely neighborhood makes it an ideal place to call home. Don't miss the chance to embrace the vast living space and culinary delights that come with this address – seize the opportunity to make it your own!
